  <data name="checkBox_RetrySleep.ToolTip" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Wait time between retries

Fixed value:
• 5: wait 5 seconds per retry
• http:3: wait 3 seconds for HTTP retry
• fragment:2: wait 2 seconds for fragment retry

Linear growth mode (arithmetic progression):
Syntax: linear=START[:END[:STEP]]
• linear=1: start at 1, add 1 sec per retry
• linear=1:10: start at 1, add 1 sec per retry, cap at 10 sec
• linear=2:20:3: start at 2, add 3 sec per retry, cap at 20 sec

Exponential growth mode (geometric progression):
Syntax: exp=START[:END[:BASE]]
Nth retry wait time = START * (BASE^(N-1))
Or more precisely: BASE^(N-1), clamped between START and END
• exp=1: basic exponential growth (2^N)
• exp=1:30: exponential growth (2^N) capped at 30 sec
• exp=5:200:2: exponential growth (5 × 2^N) capped at 200 sec</value>
